Package: linkedCells
Type: Package
Title: Reactive Cell Linking Framework for Shiny Tables
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Indranil", "Gayen", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "indranil.gayen@example.com")
Description: A framework for building interactive, constraint-based editable tables
    in Shiny. Define custom cell-linking logic to automatically update dependent
    cells when users edit values. Supports async computation, batch editing, and
    reactive constraint propagation.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
